title: Active@ File Recovery Professional 14.5.0.0 Portable
description:
****************************************************
Active@ File Recovery Professional 14.5.0.0 Portable
****************************************************

- This is a fully functional (registered) version of Active@ File Recovery Professional 14.5.0.0, including Active@ Disk Editor.
- Created with VMware ThinApp
- Language: en-US
- Size: 30 MB extracted
- Application data stored in the same directory as the application (no writing to local machine / local registry)
- OS: 32-bit/64-bit versions of Windows 8, 7, Vista, Server 2012, Server 2008, Server 2003, XP

Active@ File Recovery for Windows provides the ability to effectively detect and recover files and disks lost due to accidental deletion, disk formatting, virus and other reasons.

The Professional package also includes integrated Active@ Disk Editor (or Hex Viewer - a utility for low-level data inspection), Virtual RAID reconstructor, being able to recover damaged RAID disk arrays, and File Organizer needed to re-organize and rename files detected by their signatures.

Homepage	http://www.file-recovery.com/
